            "title": "<p>1500W Peak Motor</p>",
            "content": "<p>Reliable Power When You Need It<br/>The G26’s 1500W peak motor delivers smooth support for commutes, recreational rides, and moderate climbs. It is powerful enough to make daily riding easier while still keeping the bike efficient and easy to control.</p>",
