            "image_pos": "left",
            "title": "<p>26\" x 2.0\" Tires</p>",
            "content": "<p>Efficient Rolling with Mountain Bike Control<br/>The 26-inch tire setup gives the G26 a classic mountain bike feel. The tires are efficient on pavement and stable enough for gravel paths, bike trails, and mixed riding conditions.</p>",
