            "title": "<p>Precision Disc Brakes</p>",
            "content": "<p>Stop with Confidence<br/>The G26’s precision disc brakes provide consistent braking control for city streets, bike paths, and downhill sections. They are designed to help riders feel more secure in everyday conditions.</p>",
